Package org.apache.drill.exec.record.metadata

Class AbstractPropertied

java.lang.Object
org.apache.drill.exec.record.metadata.AbstractPropertied
All Implemented Interfaces:
Propertied
Direct Known Subclasses:
AbstractColumnMetadata, TupleSchema
public class AbstractPropertied extends Object implements Propertied
Base class for an object with properties. Defers property map creation until needed, since most instances may not need properties.
